description	"Palace Guard

^2Weaponry:
- ELG-3A Diplomat's Pistol (2)
- CR-2 Repeating Pistol (3)
- Sonic Grenade	(1)

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcements (1)
- Rally

The Palace guards were more experienced than average Naboo guards, and were tasked with the highly important task of guarding the capital of Naboo and the palace itself, and were some of the most skilled security officers."

